{"tid":1754534,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[新區議員入黎]我地會全力投票，但請你地全力攏絡人心","createTime":"2019-11-25T08:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T08:58:11.000Z","uid":63045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d829b3c5e5ffce5c11b5a13e570570c369bfe07b","tid":1754534,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"贏一次係唔夠，要keep住贏先有用！<br />\n長遠黎講立會係一條重要戰線，重要性唔使多講啦<br />\n今次其實比共產黨摸左我地底，我地陣營似乎無乜票數增長空間，會投既應該都投晒，只有海外手足番香港投票同今明兩年滿十八歲個堆。<br />\n所以今年區議會當選者，一定要做好你既工作，用盡一切手法攏絡人心，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>因為你吸到對家一票，你同對家係會拉開兩票距離。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n放心我地絕對會創造一次7成以上投票率，但各位區議員都要努力將對家納入成為自己支持者<br />\n我地要一齊努力先可以打破依加既六比四，變成七比三！"},{"pid":"cc4cabc1719f0f18f2493d0d9df6a8599175eac1","tid":1754534,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:54:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依家我哋區選贏咗，外國好關注我哋！<br />\n係咪連少少嘢都唔肯做呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n最新的tweets 一定響bot <br />\n總之<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> Retweet Like Reply </span></span>就得<br />\n㩒入👉 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=fa118af8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSen. Marco Rubio<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=5e7771b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&h=2dc87735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Ric